description:
Star Wars: The Bad Batch is entering its season one endgame with the help of the Pykes and a new antagonist: Roland Durand. Omega and the squad help Cid to reclaim her tiny throne, while referencing Star Wars, Indiana Jones, Ahsoka Tano, and the classic trilogy.
